launchpad.heading: What do you want to achieve today?
launchpad.description: Choose a starting point and we'll guide you through the best steps to take.
launchpad.pi.heading: Professional Invoicing
launchpad.pi.tagline: It's more than just a way to say 'pay me'
launchpad.pi.description: The care and detail you put into invoicing can do wonders for your brand and future business. Take these quick actions to show customers the best you have to offer.
launchpad.bbk.heading: Better Bookkeeping
launchpad.bbk.tagline: It's more than just a way to say 'pay me'
launchpad.bbk.description: Bookkeeping doesn't have to be daunting - say hello to simpler tax filing and deeper insights. Our machine learning and automation do the heavy lifting as you handle these quick actions.
launchpad.pi.card.title: Professional Invoicing
launchpad.pi.card.description: Create customizable documents that get you paid faster.

launchpad.pi.c1.popup.heading: Creating Invoices
launchpad.pi.c1.popup.paragraph: Get started with invoicing by building a reusable template. You can even add your company's logo and brand colors. Then use this template to easily create invoices.
launchpad.pi.c1.popup.bp1: Starting from scratch? Read our step-by-step invoice guide.
launchpad.pi.c1.popup.bp2: Invoice on the go with our mobile app for iOS and Android
launchpad.pi.ce.popup.heading: Creating Quotations
launchpad.pi.ce.popup.paragraph: Making quotations is simple: Add pricing information and your customer's detail and you're all set. You can email it right away or save it for later.
launchpad.pi.ce.popup.bp1: Make a professional first impression on new customers.
launchpad.pi.ce.popup.bp2: Show your pricing and payment terms upfront.
launchpad.pi.ce.popup.bp3: Easily convert quotations to invoices in Wave
launchpad.bbk.card.title: Better Bookkeeping
launchpad.bbk.card.description: Automatically sync transactions for deeper insights
launchpad.bbk.cbc.popup.heading: Connect your bank or credit card
launchpad.bbk.cbc.popup.subheading: Why is it a good idea?
launchpad.bbk.cbc.popup.paragraph: Connect securely in seconds with your online banking credentials and start automating your bookkeeping
launchpad.bbk.cbc.popup.bp1: The benefits of accounting begin with capturing transactions.
launchpad.bbk.cbc.popup.bp2: Machine learning works for you by automating categorization.
launchpad.bbk.cbc.popup.bp3: Reports provide meaningful insights and help you make better business decisions.
launchpad.bbk.mt.popup.heading: Manage Transactions
launchpad.bbk.mt.popup.paragraph: You're the expert when it comes to your business. Categorizing transactions shows you where your money is going, and Wave learns your preferences so you do fewer things manually.
launchpad.bbk.mt.popup.bp1: Create new, customized categories in seconds right from the transactions page.
launchpad.bbk.mt.popup.bp2: Easily add sales taxes or categorize multiple transactions with our bulk categorization feature.
launchpad.bbk.mt.popup.bp3: Split transactions into multiple categories to accurately record elements like fees and interest.
launchpad.bbk.ast.popup.heading: Add sales taxes
launchpad.bbk.ast.popup.paragraph: Include sales tax automatically on estimates and invoices, and track them on expenses too. Our sales tax reports summarize everything for you, so you always know where you stand.
launchpad.bbk.ast.popup.bp1: Customize sales taxes on each invoice or expense.
launchpad.bbk.ast.popup.bp2: Indicate if a tax is recoverable or compounding.
launchpad.bbk.ast.popup.bp3: Include your tax ID on invoices for easy customer reference.
launchpad.bbk.cs.popup.heading: Customize your accounts
launchpad.bbk.cs.popup.paragraph: Your chart of account is the foundation of better bookkeeping. Make it work for you by customizing it your needs. We've started you off with categories based on your business type.
launchpad.bbk.cs.popup.bp1: Understand how your business spends and earns money.
launchpad.bbk.cs.popup.bp2: Make informed decisions: know in advance if you need to shift financial priorities.
launchpad.bbk.cs.popup.bp3: Read more about how accounts and categories work.

common.hr.reports.FS.subheading: Get a clear picture of how your business is doing. Use these core statements to better understand your financial health.
common.hr.reports.FS.sectionHeading.subH: Shows your business’s net profit and summarizes your revenues and expenses in a given time period.
common.hr.reports.FS.sectionHeading2.sub: A snapshot of your finances on a given day. The balance sheet calculates your business’s worth (equity by subtracting what you owe (liabilities) from what you own (assets).
common.hr.reports.FS.sectionHeading3.sub: Shows how much money is entering and leaving your business. The cash flow statement tells you how much cash you have on hand for a specific time period.
common.hr.reports.Taxes.subheading: A detailed look at the taxes you owe based on sales taxes collected and paid, and transactions processed.
common.hr.reports.Taxes.sectionHeading.s: A breakdown of taxes collected from sales and paid on purchases. You can use this information to prepare sales tax returns and calculate your balance or refund.
common.hr.reports.Payroll.subheading: Track payroll costs including employee wages and benefits/deductions, and your payroll tax liabilities.
common.hr.reports.Payroll.sectionHeading: A breakdown of employee wage and payroll tax amounts.
Amounts added to or deducted from your employees’ regular wages. Includes information for year-end reporting.
common.hr.reports.Customers.subheading: Stay on top of overdue invoices and identify high-value or late-paying customers.
common.hr.reports.Customers.sectionHeadi: A breakdown of paid and unpaid income for every customer.

common.hr.reports.Vendors.subheading: Track your business spending. See where your money goes, and how much you owe to vendors.
common.hr.reports.Vendors.sectionHeading: A breakdown of purchases and bills from every vendor.
Unpaid and overdue bills for the last 30, 60, and 90+ days.
common.hr.reports.DR.subheading: Dig into the details of your business’s transactions, balances,and accounts.
common.hr.reports.DR.sectionHeading.subH: Summary view of balances and activity for all accounts.
common.hr.reports.DR.sectionHeading1.sub: The sum of debits and credits for all accounts on a single day. Helps you check for discrepancies to ensure your accounts balance.
common.hr.reports.DR.sectionHeading2.sub: Your complete financial activity: A detailed list of all transactions and totals for every account in your Chart of Accounts.
